            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> (ST) In Christi nomine. <persName ref="#people/239">Otto</persName> grada
                        Dei <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus, anno imperii eius Deo
                        propicio decimo, mense madius, indicione sex[ta]. Constat me <persName
                            ref="#people/4682" key="#Lombard #grandparentOf #mundualdusOf"
                            >Atta</persName> filia quondam <persName><name ref="Atto"
                            >Attoni</name></persName> de loco <placeName>Buinago</placeName>, qui
                        professa sum ex nacione mea <rs key="#Lombard">legiem vivere
                            Langobardorum</rs>, consenciente mihi cui supra Attani et subter
                        confirmante <persName ref="#people/4683" key="#grandchildOf #mundualdusOf"
                            >Rotepaldo</persName>
                        <rs key="#grandchildOf">abiatico</rs> et <rs key="#mundualdusOf"
                            >mundoaldo</rs> meo per consensum et largetatem <persName
                            key="#parentOf"><name ref="Wilielmus">Wilielmi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">genitoris</rs> [eiu]s accepissem sicuti et in presencia
                        testium accepi ad te <persName><name ref="Armaldus"
                            >Armaldo</name></persName> fil(io) quondam item <persName><name
                                ref="Armaldus">Armaldi</name></persName> de loco
                            <placeName>Camisano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Price">argentum denarios bonos libras centum</rs>, finitum precium
                        pro cuntis <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs> et <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs> seu
                        capella atque omnibus rebus illis iuris mei quam abere visa sum in locas et
                            <rs key="#Fundi">fun[da]s </rs><placeName><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae" ref="#estates/4214"
                            >Lavate</geogName></placeName>, tam infra castro quamque et foris,
                                <placeName><geogName key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4215">Virdello</geogName></placeName>,
                                <placeName><geogName key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4216">Almine</geogName></placeName>,
                                <placeName><geogName key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4217">Stagiano</geogName></placeName> et infra <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/10">Bergamo</placeName>, et <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinas</rs> duas que sunt edi[fi]catas in <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers">Brembo</placeName>, <placeName><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae" ref="#estates/4218"
                                >Caravagio</geogName></placeName>, <placeName><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae" ref="#estates/4219"
                                >Vigolongo</geogName></placeName> et super fluvio <placeName
                            ref="#places/4404">Oleo</placeName> in loco et fundo
                                <placeName><geogName key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4220">Pariatico</geogName></placeName> seu super
                        fluvio <placeName ref="#places/1981">Addua</placeName> in[fr]a <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/262">Laude</placeName> vel foris in loco et fundo
                                <placeName><geogName ref="#estates/4221"
                                key="#Houses #Fundi #Petiae">Permenugo</geogName></placeName>, et
                            <rs key="#Slave_labour">servis et ancillis </rs>similiter iuris mei,
                        nominative illis rebus omnibus, servis [et] ancillis que mihi cui supra
                        Attani obvenit per <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartula donacionis</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Morgengabe">morgincap</rs> ad condam Eremberto de suprascripto
                        loco Lavate, qui fuit <rs key="#marriage">vir meus</rs> [omn]ia et ex
                        omnibus quantum mihi per ipse due cartule obvenit et in earum legitur in
                        integrum. Que autem suprascriptis casis et castro seu omnibus rebus illis
                        [iuri]s mei superius dictis unacum acesionibus et ingressoras earum seu cum
                        superioribus et inferioribus suis, qualiter superius legitur, in integrum
                        [a]b ac die tibi cui supra Armaldi suprascripto precio vendo, trado et
                        mancipo, nuli alii venditis, donatis, alienatis, obnoxiatis, traditis nisi
                        tibi, et facias exinde a presenti die tu et heredibus tuis aut cui vos
                        dederitis iure proprietario nomine quod volueritis sine omni mea et heredum
                        meorum contradicione. Quidem et spondeo atque promitto me ego qui supra Atta
                        unacum meis heredes tibi cui supra Armaldi tuisque heredibus aut cui vos
                        dederitis suprascriptam vend(icionem), qualiter superius legitur, in imegrum
                        ab omni ornine defen[s]are. Qui si defendere non potuerimus aut si vobis
                        exinde aliquid per quovis ingenium subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs
                            key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> suprascripta vend(ita) vobis restituamus,
                        sicut pro tempore fuerit melioratas aut valuerint sub estimacio[n]e in
                        consimiles locas. Actum loco <placeName>Gabiano</placeName>. [S]ignum +
                        manus suprascripte Attani qui anc cartam vindicionis fieri rogavi ut supra.
                        [S]ignum + manus suprascripto Rotepaldi qui eadem Atta avia et mundoalda sua
                        consensci ut supra. Signum + manus suprascripto Wilielmi qui eidem Rotepaldi
                        filio [subscripsit ut supra]. [Si]gnum +++ manibus <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Bonipertus">Boniperti</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Dachipertus">Daiverti</name></persName> seu
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Garibertus"
                            >Gariverti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (ST) <persName key="#Notary #Judge"><name
                                ref="Dachipertus">Dagibertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palacii
                        scripsi, post tradita complevi et dedi.</ab>
